name: skill-builder
description: |
  [WHAT] Skill creation and documentation codification router
  [HOW] Routes to codifier workflow (scrape/analyze/package docs) or skill-creator (author new skills) based on intent
  [WHEN] Use when converting existing docs to skills, creating new skills from scratch, or combining/merging existing skills
  [WHY] Unifies doc-to-skill conversion with new skill authoring under single entry point

  Triggers: "create a skill from docs", "codify documentation", "convert docs to skill", "make this documentation searchable",
            "make a skill", "create a skill", "combine a skill", "new skill", "skill from scratch", "codify", "skill-builder"

  Routes:
  - Documentation → codifier workflow (scrape, analyze, package)
  - New skill authoring → skill-creator (standards, structure, progressive disclosure)
  - Skill combination → both (analyze existing + author merged)
